{"title":"和平幸福的保证  为签订中苏友好互助条约而作","authors":["萧松煜"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平幸福的保证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为签订中苏友好互助条约而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧松煜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个巨人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握着手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼炉里打成的钢筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手紧紧握在一起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的城堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在全世界的人们面前筑成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的眼睛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联人民在跳跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的眼睛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华儿女在奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东看着斯大林！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林看着毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨人的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里就歌声奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声变成音符；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符变成字形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符奏出心底的共鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字形写出嘴里的和声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是平常的“条约”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是平常的“协定”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最恰当的名称——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人类和平幸福的保证”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的走狗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑拨战争的罪犯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这歌声使你们耸肩发抖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这城堡使你们畏缩不敢上前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个巨人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热手握着热手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个巨人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈颜对着慈颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二，十七"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}